        "TileImage": "$($repository 9ee7b5bc-2a0a-4303-bcaf-4fcce64022cb).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. The ICA has taken a mission order from the client named &quot;Eclipscycle&quot;. His orders are to eliminate anyone who has taken  viewers away from his livestreams. You will be heading to Sapienza to start, and I suggest looking high and low for anyone taking up anyone&apos;s attention. Good luck, and happy hunting, 47.",
